        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 20 - 65 years

          -  Operated and non operated colorectal cancer patients

          -  Patient administering mFOLFOX 6 ( Folinic acid 400 mg/m2 1 day, oxaliplatin 85 mg/m2 1
             day, 5-fluorouracil 400 mg/m2 bolus 2400 mg/m2 continuous infusion 48 hours)

        Exclusion Criteria:

